A.MPLS AToM connect R4-R5

r4
int eth 0/0
ip add 10.45.45.4 255.255.255.0
no sh
int loo 0
ip add 10.4.4.4 255.255.255.0
router eigrp 45
network 10.0.0.0

r5
int eth 0/0
ip add 10.45.45.5 255.255.255.0
no sh
int loo 0
ip add 10.5.5.5 255.255.255.0
router eigrp 45
network 10.0.0.0

